    <item>
      <title>阿联酋协议推动埃及债券上涨，黑市英镑上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/egyptian-pound-gains-on-black-market-dollar-bonds-jump-most-on-record</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及的美元债券飙升，英镑在街头交易中走强，与阿拉伯联合酋长国达成的具有里程碑意义的 350 亿美元投资协议激发了人们对这个现金短缺的国家将渡过经济危机的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/egyptian-pound-gains-on-black-market-dollar-bonds-jump-most-on-record</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 26 Feb 2024 15:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃尔顿家族在股价上涨后出售 15 亿美元的沃尔玛股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-26/walton-family-sells-1-5-billion-of-walmart-stock-after-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周末，随着股价徘徊在历史高位附近，沃尔顿家族成员出售了价值约 15 亿美元的沃尔玛公司股票。]]></description>
